# AI Sales Outreach Agent — Implementation Plan

A multi-agent AI sales automation system that researches prospects, generates hyper-personalized outreach emails, sends via Gmail, tracks replies, and updates a CRM — all orchestrated autonomously.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Keys Required** — You will need to provide API keys for:
> - **OpenAI** (`OPENAI_API_KEY`) — for LLM-powered email generation
> - **Tavily** (`TAVILY_API_KEY`) — for web search / prospect research
> - **Gmail** (`credentials.json`) — OAuth2 credentials from Google Cloud Console
> - **Notion** (`NOTION_API_KEY` + database ID) or **Airtable** — for CRM
>
> The system will work with placeholder/mock modes for local development without keys.

> [!WARNING]
> **Gmail API requires OAuth2 setup.** You must create a project in Google Cloud Console, enable the Gmail API, and download `credentials.json`. The first run will open a browser for authorization.

---

## Architecture Overview

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  FastAPI Backend                     │
│  /api/prospects  /api/campaigns  /api/analytics      │
├──────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────┤
│    LangGraph Agent   │      Vector Memory           │
│    Orchestrator      │      (ChromaDB)              │
├──────┬───────┬───────┼───────┬──────────────────────┤
│Research│Email │Gmail  │Reply  │  CRM Agent           │
│Agent   │Agent │Agent  │Track  │  (Notion/Airtable)   │
│(Tavily)│(LLM) │(API)  │Agent  │                      │
└──────┴───────┴───────┴───────┴──────────────────────┘
         ↕               ↕              ↕
    Web Search       Gmail API      Notion API
```

---

