### Database & Memory Layer

#### [NEW] [app/models.py](file:///c:/Users/nihan/Desktop/AI%20Sales%20Outreach%20Agent/app/models.py)
Pydantic models: `Prospect`, `Campaign`, `OutreachEmail`, `CRMRecord`, `AgentState`.

#### [NEW] [app/memory.py](file:///c:/Users/nihan/Desktop/AI%20Sales%20Outreach%20Agent/app/memory.py)
ChromaDB vector store wrapper — stores past interactions, research data, and email history for contextual memory across agent runs.

#### [NEW] [app/database.py](file:///c:/Users/nihan/Desktop/AI%20Sales%20Outreach%20Agent/app/database.py)
SQLite-based local storage via SQLAlchemy for prospects, campaigns, and outreach tracking.

---

### Agent System (LangGraph)

#### [NEW] [app/agents/orchestrator.py](file:///c:/Users/nihan/Desktop/AI%20Sales%20Outreach%20Agent/app/agents/orchestrator.py)
LangGraph `StateGraph` that defines the agent pipeline:
1. **research** → 2. **generate_email** → 3. **send_email** → 4. **update_crm** → 5. **track_reply**

Conditional edges for retry logic, human-in-the-loop approval, and error handling.

#### [NEW] [app/agents/research_agent.py](file:///c:/Users/nihan/Desktop/AI%20Sales%20Outreach%20Agent/app/agents/research_agent.py)
Uses Tavily API to search for company info, prospect LinkedIn/social profiles, recent news, tech stack, and funding data. Stores results in vector memory.

#### [NEW] [app/agents/email_agent.py](file:///c:/Users/nihan/Desktop/AI%20Sales%20Outreach%20Agent/app/agents/email_agent.py)
Uses OpenAI to generate hyper-personalized outreach emails based on research data. Supports multiple tones (professional, casual, consultative) and follow-up sequences.

#### [NEW] [app/agents/gmail_agent.py](file:///c:/Users/nihan/Desktop/AI%20Sales%20Outreach%20Agent/app/agents/gmail_agent.py)
Gmail API integration — authenticates via OAuth2, sends emails, checks for replies in threads, and reports delivery status.

#### [NEW] [app/agents/crm_agent.py](file:///c:/Users/nihan/Desktop/AI%20Sales%20Outreach%20Agent/app/agents/crm_agent.py)
Updates Notion database (or Airtable) with prospect status, outreach history, reply tracking, and pipeline stage.

#### [NEW] [app/agents/reply_tracker.py](file:///c:/Users/nihan/Desktop/AI%20Sales%20Outreach%20Agent/app/agents/reply_tracker.py)
Polls Gmail for thread replies, classifies sentiment (positive/negative/neutral) via LLM, and triggers follow-up actions.

